{"tid":102440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[molamola] 自動填顏色o既A.I.面世了!","createTime":"2017-01-31T15:40:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-03T12:12:00.000Z","uid":22675,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"17210a0f79e00930af56c951cc5e546737cabbc5","tid":102440,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:40:42.000Z","msg":"<strong>繪師必看《PaintsChainer》塗色苦手的福音 <br />\n人工智慧來幫你上色</strong><br />\n<br />\n阿珂 2017.01.30 <br />\n<br />\n對於繪師來說絕對是一大福音啦！雖然偷懶，但如果只是隨手撇撇的塗鴉也能簡單上色更有完整感，或是在上之前先請機器幫你把大概的顏色舖好以看看視覺效果如何，都是相當不錯用的網路工具！最近這個人工智慧上色的網站服務《PaintsChainer》在繪畫界的網友之間相當流行，因為只要簡單幾個步驟，這個網站就能幫你的黑白線稿上色，用過的都說厲害耶！<br />\n<br />\nPaintsChainer是一項幫你上色的網路工具，目前在GitHub已經開源，或許在經過更多高手加持、擴充演算之後變得能夠更加厲害，不過目前表現的效果就已經蠻讓人驚豔的了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/27/60/paCZoqSak6earaSd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F27%2F60%2FpaCZoqSak6earaSd.jpg&h=9d66937a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片來自：Qiita<br />\n<br />\n操作也很簡單不困難，網站目前支援一般jpg或png的圖檔，選好線稿上傳之後，就可以選擇是要自己下顏色指示，或是乾脆就讓網站自己幫你決定顏色。"},{"pid":"113656e773a0637b326d6f391c72b2ba3d9c12a6","tid":102440,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:41:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/27/60/paCZoqSak6earKY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F27%2F60%2FpaCZoqSak6earKY.jpg&h=9d2bf5eb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n圖片來自：Qiita <br />\n<br />\n按下colorize就幫你上色溜！ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/27/60/paCZoqSak6eaq6U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F27%2F60%2FpaCZoqSak6eaq6U.jpg&h=205f7f25&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n圖片來自：Qiita <br />\n<br />\n不過PaintsChainer充其量也就是舖色的程度而已，光影變化還是得靠各位自己努力，對於那種總是覺得黑白線稿還不錯，但自己上色就會搞砸的人，有這樣幫忙配色、上色的網站真是幫了大忙啦～！<br />\n<br />\n還有繪師感慨「比我自己上色還漂亮啊...」 <br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/27/60/paCZoqSalJ6craU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F27%2F60%2FpaCZoqSalJ6craU.jpg&h=8b51b61b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n沒有指定顏色也會自動判定該上膚色的地方，還知道死庫水要深藍色...這技術真的很神秘！ <br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/27/60/paCZoqSalJ6craQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F27%2F60%2FpaCZoqSalJ6craQ.jpg&h=0f1bb8e1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"https://news.gamme.com.tw/1472760\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.gamme.com.tw%2F1472760&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=867ed33c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.gamme.com.tw/1472760</a>"},{"pid":"9f178cc7b4ebea38bf512dd4e2661dfcfaf04365","tid":102440,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:42:07.000Z","msg":"designer的好幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57304ad5ae669039cabd126b397c536e1d01cc3d","tid":102440,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:44:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>designer的好幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要失業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbae743e4a6a2dfbfae434153e7cda9d8b6a7765","tid":102440,"uid":54163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:46:04.000Z","msg":"AI距離取代人類又踏前一步"},{"pid":"82cd344079bd384335c2eb1fc24bdc517e5d00bc","tid":102440,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T00:16:46.000Z","msg":"袁生d作品有救"},{"pid":"e0ad6e20c25ec7cc7bff40d664ee7bcf9c357487","tid":102440,"uid":34896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T00:36:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>袁生d作品有救</blockquote><br />\n畫好d線先講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=